OL,3,CScientists investigating 'alarming
OL,4,Crise' in a type of cancer affecting
OL,5,Cunder-50s
OL,7,FA team at King's College London is
OL,8,Fworking alongside nine other
OL,9,Finstitutions around the world to look
OL,10,Fat how the cancer develops in its
OL,11,Fearly stages.
OL,13,FSamples will be analysed from diverse
OL,14,Fpopulations and it's hoped new
OL,15,Femphasis can be placed on preventing
OL,16,Fcancer developing.
OL,18,FProfessor Tim Spector, Director of
OL,19,FTwinsUK at King's College London and
OL,20,Fscientific co-founder at ZOE, said:
