OL,12,FDr Sheeba Irshad at King's College
OL,13,FLondon added: "There is a growing
OL,14,Frecognition of the impact of
OL,15,Fenvironmental exposures and ancestry-
OL,16,Frelated factors on tumor biology.
OL,18,F"However, our understanding is not yet
OL,19,Fcomprehensive enough to make a
OL,20,Fsignificant impact on improving
OL,21,Foutcomes for ethnic minorities.
